{
  "text": "CDV has also been found in naturally infected noncanine hosts [CITATION_1] and recent dramatic outbreaks in breeding colonies of rhesus macaques (Macaca mulatta) and cynomolgus macaques (Macaca fascicularis), has drawn attention of a possible zoonosis in the post-measles eradication times [CITATION_2] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "32455830",
